# Marketing Analytics Dashboard - Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your actual values:

```env
# Supabase Configuration
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_supabase_anon_key_here

# Google OAuth Configuration
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=your_google_client_secret_here

# Facebook/Meta Configuration
VITE_FACEBOOK_APP_ID=your_facebook_app_id_here
VITE_FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET=your_facebook_app_secret_here

# GoHighLevel Configuration
VITE_GHL_CLIENT_ID=your_ghl_client_id_here
VITE_GHL_CLIENT_SECRET=your_ghl_client_secret_here

# Application Configuration
VITE_APP_URL=http://localhost:5173
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000
VITE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URL=https://your-domain.com/oauth/callback
VITE_DEFAULT_DOMAIN=https://your-domain.com
VITE_DEFAULT_LOCATION_ID=your_default_location_id

# Optional: Environment
NODE_ENV=development

# Optional: Debug logging
DEBUG=marketing-analytics:*
```

## Required Environment Variables

### Supabase
- `VITE_SUPABASE_URL`: Your Supabase project URL
- `VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`: Your Supabase anonymous key

### Google OAuth
- `VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID`: Google OAuth client ID
- `VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET`: Google OAuth client secret

### Facebook/Meta
- `VITE_FACEBOOK_APP_ID`: Facebook App ID
- `VITE_FACEBOOK_APP_SECRET`: Facebook App Secret

### GoHighLevel
- `VITE_GHL_CLIENT_ID`: GoHighLevel OAuth client ID
- `VITE_GHL_CLIENT_SECRET`: GoHighLevel OAuth client secret

### Application Settings
- `VITE_APP_URL`: Your application URL (for development)
- `VITE_API_BASE_URL`: Your API base URL
- `VITE_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URL`: OAuth callback URL
- `VITE_DEFAULT_DOMAIN`: Default domain for URL processing
- `VITE_DEFAULT_LOCATION_ID`: Default GoHighLevel location ID

## Security Notes

- Never commit this file to version control
- Keep your API keys secure and private
- Use environment variables in production
- Rotate your API keys regularly
- Use different keys for development and production
